Performance Guitar Picks for Acoustic Guitar – Non-Slip Raised Thumb/Finger Rest – 3 Gauges in One Guitar Pick for Multiple Tones – Electric Guitar Picks – Guitar Picks with Style
[' GUITAR PICKS WITH UNIQUE STYLE: The unique, triangular shape gives our guitar picks a distinctive look that make them stand out from ordinary guitar picks. Contrasting stylish black and white acoustic and electric guitar picks: black for the sad songs, white for the happy songs. Two of each because they’re picks, you know you’re going to lose one sooner or later:-)', 'NO  HERE WITH A RAISED THUMB AND FINGER REST: These guitar picks have a raised, curved thumb & finger rest on each side of the pick to give you an effortless, non-slip grip. Whilst the guitar pick itself is smooth, the raised thumb and finger rest area is slightly coarse to further help reduce slipping. This allows a more comfortable, relaxed grip on the pick for better, flexible contact with the guitar’s strings.', 'THREE  GUITAR PICK SOUNDS IN ONE PICK: Each pick has a light (0.5mm), medium (0.75mm) and heavy (1mm) gauge picking corner for distinct guitar sounds in one unique guitar pick. Use the heavy gauge corner for warmer, softer tones, great for melodic acoustic guitar strumming. The light gauge gives a crisper sound for articulate picking. For more variety try each pick corner at different points on the strings. NOTE: All four picks have the same three gauge-widths.', 'A SOLID GUITAR PICK TO PERFORM WITH CONFIDENCE: Unless you lose it of course, we can’t help you with that. Made with a PC+ ABS thermoplastic blend for the best of both strength (don’t you hate it when the corner of your pick can’t handle the pressure and snaps right off, no cracking or splitting here) and flexibility (just as we hate it when a pick is too hard and doesn’t strum easily).', 'NOT YOUR ORDINARY PICK – GUITAR IN STYLE: the slightly different shape and raised finger rest does take just a bit of getting used to. A small sacrifice to play for a unique, durable pick that makes you look cool and sound cool. Guitar in Style!']
